\">οὐδὲ λύκοι τε καὶ ἄρνες ὁμόφρονα θ. ἔχουσιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:263\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.263</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἕτερος δέ με θ. ἔρυκε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:302\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.302</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐμὸν θ. ἔπειθεν</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:33\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">33</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">θωπείας κολακικάς, αἳ . . τοὺς θ. ποιοῦσιν κηρίνους</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:633d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">633d</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n49415.7\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">spirit, courage</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μένος καὶ θ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:20:174\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.174</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">θ. ἐνὶ στήθεσσι λαβεῖν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:10:461\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.461</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign